{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534493849&di=a2576cb078942f53fa5255978eccdf79&src=http%3A%2F%2Fa.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2Ffaedab64034f78f0a79931df71310a55b3191c0f.jpg","summary":"哈尔滨广厦学院(Guangsha College)，简称“广厦学院”，位于美丽的北国冰城哈尔滨市，是经国家教育部批准的民办全日制本科普通综合类高等学校。2000年8月，经黑龙江省政府批准，由北京中科俊泰投资有限责任公司独立投资，创建在哈尔滨市江北利民开发区的第一所民办高校，建校初期名称为“黑龙江广厦学院”(专修)；其后，学校先后与哈尔滨理工大学、哈尔滨商业大学合作办学，更名为“哈尔滨理工大学广厦学院”、“哈尔滨商业大学广厦学院”；2012年3月，终止与哈尔商业大学合作办学，学院易名为哈尔滨广厦学院，成为民办普通高等学校，具有学士学位授予权力。截至2018年1月，学校占地面积45.72万㎡；设有5个二级学院，学科涵盖工学、经济学、管理学、艺术学、文学、理学等多个学科门类；全日制在校生近8000人。","tags":["综合类","本科","民办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"2000","所在地区":"黑龙江省哈尔滨市利民开发区学院路1号","院校隶属":"黑龙江教育厅"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493849&di=5e49ef4f70c9d231931d044debda934b&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3726779059%2C964926680%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493849&di=a7462238546ceb337b59f3ccf3293d75&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3372505332%2C3825400335%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493849&di=69292328a1902ed2f4cfd81742c68122&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3727801426%2C978854687%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493849&di=0af70f8c7364f3d9c298fd1d038fdcfd&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3572855313%2C792810145%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493849&di=67b05bc501f774913074d8b69ebb44c0&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3326419314%2C3010891036%26fm%3D179%26app%3D42%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D300%26h%3D300","https:/